data.description: This move-in ready home was renovated just 4 years ago and comes equipped with Vivint security system. During the renovation, the A/C unit, water heater, kitchen countertops, floors, and electrical panel were all replaced along with so much more. Downstairs you will find a beautiful family room/den to relax and entertain guests. This home is located in a quiet neighborhood not far from the highway and shopping. Schedule your appointment today, you don't wanna miss the opportunity to make this your home.
